description:
"In my black skin I can be________!", is a picture book that portrays black men and women in various occupations/professions. Showing our children that, they can be whatever aspire and want to be. Teach them that no one can tell them, that they cannot become what they want or dream to be.
Educate, Encourage and Inspire our children.

name: "my black hair is Natural..." tee
description:
Our black skin comes in a variety of shades, so I decided to do something new with the "Natural" tees. Every shirt will not be the same, as our skin tone is not the same. I "INDIVIDUALLY" mix several colors of inks to get various shades and colors.
As, I post pictures to the page just watch for the different shades and colors that are in the shirts and the ladies in them.

Shirts are 95% cotton and 5% spandex babydoll Fitted tees.

NO TWO PRINTS/COLORS WILL BE THE SAME!

Please contact me at myblackskinis@gmail.com or at (323) 216 1519, to notify me of your color choices.
Thank you, 
Eugene A. Slusher


These are the colors that you can choose from:
Black
Kelly Green
Pink
Golden Yellow
Orange
Bright Red
Red Shimmer
Metallic Blue
Blue Shimmer
Light Blue
White
Glow in the Dark Neon

You can pick up to three colors. 
Please add your three colors at checkout or in the notes section. 

If you would like the foil overlay or rhinestones added to your tee, you now have the option to add it to your tee.
